!! Title: Glass Wedge Lens
!! Category: Isolated Command
!! Keywords: WEDGE, LENSES
!! Description: A wedge of glass made
!! with LENSES command.
!! Edit History: (latest first)
!! 10/07/2000 - cp - modified format; added description
!! 01/01/1996 - bro - creation
!!--

SYSTEM NEW
RESET 

LENSES
  WEDGE Z 0 1 BK7 20 .5

WINDOW X Z
WINDOW 1.5  !! Enlarge 50%
PLOT LENS 'LENS:WEDGE' COLORS 11
RETURN